{"id": "art-1381", "label": "Art. 1381", "title": "Art. 1381", "slug": "art-1381", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2083601287\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2244\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2083601287\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 138<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_510275078\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2243\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_510275078\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În cazul în care într-o societate pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\nare loc delegarea <span class=SpellE>atribu&#355;iilor</span> de conducere\nc&#259;tre directori, conform art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>143</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, majoritatea membrilor consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\nva fi format&#259; din administratori neexecutivi.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_447894102\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2242\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_447894102\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În <span class=SpellE>în&#355;elesul</span> prezentei <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legi</i>, membri neexecutivi ai consiliului\nde <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> sunt cei care nu au fost <span\nclass=SpellE>numi&#355;i</span> directori, în conformitate cu art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>143</span><span style='color:black'>.</span></p>"}